Algorithm-MasterMind version 0.0.3

This is a testbed for different algorithms to play
MasterMind. Theoretically, it should be easy to add your own.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install


DEPENDENCIES

None.


